The paper is about learning to rank search results, which is a task in information retrieval (IR) and falls under the cs.IR category. The paper also uses deep convolutional neural networks to extract visual semantic features from images, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models to improve ranking quality, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of text-only representations, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of multimodal representations, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
